id: pm-btwe
title: Add importer/exporter options arg and command-def examples to SDK.md
description: "PR #94 (2026-06-01) added an optional 3rd options argument to registerImporter/registerExporter enabling full command definition with flags. SDK.md has a basic registerImporter/registerExporter section (around line 478-520) but does not show the options arg for command definition, which is the primary use case for first-party packages like pm-beads and pm-todos."
type: Chore
status: open
priority: 3
