author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- SDK.md registerImporter/registerExporter section shows the optional 3rd arg with a command-definition example\n- The example includes at minimum: command name, flags, description\n- The pm-beads or pm-todos pattern is cited as a first-party reference implementation"
